Author: samema
Text: Unfortunately such a fu cking mood rn

Author: not_the_cicada
Text: You definitely are. So many of us here are so so hard on ourselves because we think we hate being “honest”. But being extra bad to ourselves is it’s own lie.   I know this feeling, and how it’s hard to believe other people, but I know in moments of lucidity that I do matter, and I know that you do too.   Sensitive people have such a hard time of it in this world 💕
